snippet.textDisplay:
How to get the secret tapes for amanda the adventurer 3
Red Tape: Enter the code 4307 to access the folder box.
Cyan Tape: Place the hamburger in front of the bottom right stasis pod. Put the ice cream in front of the second stasis pod from the right. Position the cake in front of the third stasis pod on the right. Next, place the milk in front of the back right stasis pod. Now, put the salad in front of the bottom left stasis pod. Position the sandwich in front of the second stasis pod from the left. Place the pizza in front of the third stasis pod on the left. Finally, put the sushi in front of the back left stasis pod.
Orange Tape: Type "Marcus" when Amanda asks, "What do you want to be if you grow up?"
Green Tape: Place the correct candles with their corresponding pedestals; there are four pedestals, so four corresponding candles.
snippet.textOriginal:
How to get the secret tapes for amanda the adventurer 3
Red Tape: Enter the code 4307 to access the folder box.
Cyan Tape: Place the hamburger in front of the bottom right stasis pod. Put the ice cream in front of the second stasis pod from the right. Position the cake in front of the third stasis pod on the right. Next, place the milk in front of the back right stasis pod. Now, put the salad in front of the bottom left stasis pod. Position the sandwich in front of the second stasis pod from the left. Place the pizza in front of the third stasis pod on the left. Finally, put the sushi in front of the back left stasis pod.
Orange Tape: Type "Marcus" when Amanda asks, "What do you want to be if you grow up?"
Green Tape: Place the correct candles with their corresponding pedestals; there are four pedestals, so four corresponding candles.
